  "legendsInaccurateTitle": "Inaccurate data?",
  "legendsInaccurateIntro": "Due to limitations of the Clash of Clans API, our data might not always be perfectly accurate. Here's why:\n",
  "legendsInaccurateApiDelayTitle": "1. API Delay: ",
  "legendsInaccurateApiDelayBody": "The API can take up to 5 minutes to update, causing a lag in reflecting real-time trophy changes.\n",
  "legendsInaccurateConcurrentTitle": "2. Concurrent Changes: \n",
  "legendsInaccurateMultipleAttacksTitle": "- Multiple Attacks/Defenses: ",
  "legendsInaccurateMultipleAttacksBody": "If multiple attacks or defenses happen in quick succession, the API might show combined results (e.g., +68 or -68).\n",
  "legendsInaccurateSimultaneousTitle": "- Simultaneous Attack and Defense: ",
  "legendsInaccurateSimultaneousBody": "If an attack and defense occur at the same time, you might see a mixed result (e.g., +4).\n",
  "legendsInaccurateNetGainTitle": "3. Net Gain/Loss: ",
  "legendsInaccurateNetGainBody": "Despite timing issues, the overall net gain or loss for the day is accurate. ",
  "legendsInaccurateConclusion": "These limitations are common across all tools using the Clash of Clans API. We sadly can't fix that as it is in Supercell's hands. We do our best to compensate for these limits and provide results as close to reality as possible. Thank you for understanding!",
