  "faqWhatCanBotDo": "What can the ClashKing Discord bot do?",
  "faqWhatCanBotDoAnswer": "The ClashKing Discord bot helps you manage your clan directly from Discord with comprehensive tracking tools, automated notifications, and seamless integration with this app. It's designed for clan leaders and members who want to stay connected and organized:",
  "faqInviteBotToServer": "Invite Bot to Server",
  "faqBotFeatureTracking": "Player & Clan Tracking",
  "faqBotFeatureTrackingDesc": "Add and monitor multiple clans and players with real-time updates",
  "faqBotFeatureWars": "War Management",
  "faqBotFeatureWarsDesc": "Track war performance, analyze attacks, and get war notifications",
  "faqBotFeatureNotifications": "Smart Notifications",
  "faqBotFeatureNotificationsDesc": "Get alerts for donations, war attacks, and important clan events",
  "faqBotFeatureCommands": "Powerful Commands",
  "faqBotFeatureCommandsDesc": "Use slash commands to quickly access player stats, war info, and more",
  "faqNeedHelp": "I need help or I would like to make a suggestion. How can I contact you?",
  "faqNeedHelpAnswer": "You can join our Discord Server to ask for help or to provide feedback, or you can email us at devs@clashk.ing. Please only write in English or French.",
  "faqSendEmail": "Send an email",
  "faqJoinDiscord": "Join our Discord Server",
  "faqCannotOpenMailClient": "For some reasons we can't open your mail client. We copied the email address for you. You can write an email and paste the address in the recipient field.",
  "faqTroubleshooting": "Troubleshooting",
  "faqTroubleshootingDataTitle": "Why is my data not syncing?",
  "faqTroubleshootingDataDescription": "Player or clan data appears outdated",
  "faqTroubleshootingDataSolution1": "Pull down to refresh the page",
  "faqTroubleshootingDataSolution2": "Check if your clan is tracked (see above)",
  "faqTroubleshootingDataSolution3": "Wait a few minutes and try again : the API can take some time to update",
  "faqTroubleshootingCrashTitle": "Why does the app crash?",
  "faqTroubleshootingCrashDescription": "App closes unexpectedly or freezes",
  "faqTroubleshootingCrashSolution1": "Close the app and restart it",
  "faqTroubleshootingCrashSolution2": "Update the app to the latest version",
  "faqTroubleshootingCrashSolution3": "Clear app cache and data (Android) or reinstall the app",
  "faqTroubleshootingCrashSolution4": "Free up device storage space",
  "faqContactSupport": "Contact support if problem persists (see last section)",
  "faqTroubleshootingAccountTitle": "Why can't I verify my account?",
  "faqTroubleshootingAccountDescription": "Problems linking your Clash of Clans account",
  "faqTroubleshootingAccountSolution1": "Make sure you're using the correct player tag starting with #",
  "faqTroubleshootingAccountSolution2": "If the account seems to be already linked, use the API token from Clash of Clans settings",
  "faqTroubleshootingSolutions": "Solutions:",
  "faqWhatIsClashKingProject": "What is the ClashKing project?",
  "faqWhatIsClashKingProjectAnswer": "ClashKing is an open-source Clash of Clans statistics and clan management project created by passionate players for the community. We develop this as a side project alongside our full-time jobs, driven by our love for the game. We offer a mobile app, Discord bot, and free API that work together to provide the ultimate Clash of Clans experience. The project is funded entirely through user donations and Supercell Creator code usage - no ads, no premium features!",
  "faqViewOnGitHub": "View on GitHub",
  "faqFeaturesGuide": "What can ClashKing app do?",
  "faqFeaturesGuideDescription": "Take your Clash of Clans experience to the next level! ClashKing app delivers beautiful, fast access to all your stats and clan data - perfect for players who do not have Discordand those who prefer a sleek mobile experience:",
  "faqAppDevelopmentNotice": "We're actively developing new features to make the app even better. Your feedback helps us improve!",
  "faqFeaturesPlayerTitle": "Player Statistics",
  "faqFeaturesPlayerDescription": "Track your progress, achievements, and legend league performance",
  "faqFeaturesClanTitle": "Clan Management",
  "faqFeaturesClanDescription": "Monitor clan members, donations, and overall clan health",
  "faqFeaturesWarTitle": "War Tracking",
  "faqFeaturesWarDescription": "Analyze war performance, attack strategies, and win rates",
  "faqFeaturesLegendsTitle": "Inaccurate data?",
  "faqFeaturesLegendsDescription": "Daily trophy tracking and end-of-season statistics",
  "faqFeaturesCwlTitle": "CWL Analytics",
  "faqFeaturesCwlDescription": "Clan War League performance and member contributions",
  "faqSearchHint": "Search FAQ...",
  "faqSectionGettingStarted": "Getting Started & About",
  "faqSectionSupportAndContact": "Support & Contact",
  "faqTranslationIssue": "Translation is missing or incorrect?",
  "faqTranslationIssueAnswer": "Translations are done by app users like you! We (developers) only provide French and English translations. If you find missing or incorrect translations, you can help improve them. Do not hesitate to reach out to us on Discord or via email if want to help us. We have a specific Discord channel for translators where you can ask questions and get help.",
  "faqWaysToSupport": "Ways to support us:",
  "translationHelpUsTranslate": "Help us translate",
  "translationSuggestFeatures": "Suggest features",
  "translationThankYou": "Thank you!",
  "translationThankYouContent": "A huge thank you to all our amazing translators who help us make this app accessible to more people around the world!",
  "translationHelpTranslateContent": "You can help us translate the app on Crowdin. If your language is not available on Crowdin, feel free to request it in our Discord Server. Thank you so much for your help!",
  "translationHelpTranslateButton": "Help Translate on Crowdin",
